DESCRIPTION

  Pacman96 is a very systemfriendly port of the classic Pacman.
  There is also a Leveleditor included, but unfortunately people
  seem to ignore this (until now).

  This is a Levelset for Pacman96 which makes it easy to watch
  all the nice animation sequences between the levels.

  Hopefully someone else if going to upload some more useful
  levelsets...

FEATURES

  o Even playable for children younger than three weeks!
  o Capable of Plug'n'Watch (TM)

SPECIAL REQUIREMENTS

  You need to obtain Pacman96 to play these levels. You can
  download it from `aminet:game/misc/Pacman96.lha'

