INSTALLATION

  o Drag the `ViewAnims.PacLevels' into the drawer where Pacman96 is
    located
  o Click the Pacman96-icon ONCE on Workbench, and activate
    `Icons/Information' or simple press Right-Amiga-I.
  o Add tooltype `CUSTOMLEVELS=ViewAnims.PacLevels'
  o Click `Save', and start Pacman96

    or

  o Start Pacman96 as usual
  o Select `EDITOR' from the main menu
  o Click the `L' and select `ViewAnims.PacLevels' in the file
    requester
  o Double-click the note icon to return to the main menu
  o Start game

